---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About" 
  description="Learn about Vizino Studio - mission, vision, and the team behind AI-powered design"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>About Vizino Studio</h1>
    <p>Transforming the future of interior design with artificial intelligence</p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 3rem;">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>At Vizino Studio, we believe that everyone deserves access to professional-grade design visualization tools. Our mission is to democratize interior design by combining cutting-edge AI technology with an intuitive, user-friendly platform.</p>
    <p>We empower designers, architects, and homeowners to visualize, iterate, and perfect interior spaces in minutesâ€”not weeks.</p>
  </section>

  <section style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px;">
    <h2>Our Vision</h2>
    <p>To become the leading AI-powered design platform that enables people to confidently make interior design decisions through instant, photorealistic visualizations.</p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 3rem;">
    <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>AI-First Approach</h3>
        <p>Built from the ground up with generative AI at the core, not as an afterthought.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Precision & Control</h3>
        <p>Advanced prompt optimization and granular control over every design element.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>User-Centric Design</h3>
        <p>Intuitive interface with interactive onboarding for users of all skill levels.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Flexibility First</h3>
        <p>Guest mode, free tier, API integration, and flexible credit system for all users.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Professional Workflow</h3>
        <p>Project management, space organization, and usage tracking built in.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Continuous Innovation</h3>
        <p>Regular updates with new features and improved AI models.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 3rem;">
    <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
    <p>Vizino Studio is built with modern, scalable technologies to ensure reliability and performance:</p>
    <div style="margin: 1.5rem 0; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f9f9f9; border-left: 4px solid #667eea;">
      <p><strong>Frontend:</strong> Modern web framework with responsive design for all devices</p>
      <p><strong>Backend:</strong> Scalable cloud infrastructure with API support</p>
      <p><strong>AI Engine:</strong> State-of-the-art generative AI models for image transformation</p>
      <p><strong>Database:</strong> Secure, distributed database for project and user management</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 3rem;">
    <h2 style="color: white; border-bottom-color: white;">Our Team</h2>
    <p>Vizino Studio is developed by passionate designers, engineers, and AI enthusiasts committed to transforming the interior design industry.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">We combine deep expertise in:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
      <li>Interior Design & Architecture</li>
      <li>Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning</li>
      <li>Software Engineering & Cloud Infrastructure</li>
      <li>User Experience & Interface Design</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 3rem;">
    <h2>Contact Information</h2>
    <p>Want to learn more about Vizino Studio or discuss partnerships? Reach out to our team:</p>
    <div style="margin: 2rem 0; padding: 1.5rem; background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 8px;">
      <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@vizino-studio.com">info@vizino-studio.com</a></p>
      <p><strong>Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@vizino-studio.com">support@vizino-studio.com</a></p>
      <p><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://vizino-studio.com" target="_blank">vizino-studio.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem;">
    <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
    <p>Follow Vizino Studio to stay updated on new features and design inspiration</p>
    <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
      <a href="https://twitter.com/vizino-studio" class="button" target="_blank">Follow on Twitter</a>
      <a href="https://instagram.com/vizino-studio" class="button" style="margin-left: 1rem;" target="_blank">Follow on Instagram</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
